cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.DS, cs.CY, cs.CR 

This paper deals with ranking functions on the web, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR). The concept of spammability is also related to social influence (cs.SI) and graph theory (cs.DS). The paper also discusses an algebraic structure for PageRank, which is related to computational complexity (cs.CY) and cryptography (cs.CR).
